replyContent: Hi, Thanks for the review, the free version and the paid versions both share the same mechanics. Depending on the device, it will help to slowly tilt the device up/down and make sure it is not slouching left/right when on forehead otherwise it will not detect as being on forehead. We will still issue an update to make this easier! Thanks again.
